Invocation Name: good morning
des: "Good Morning" is a dynamic app that is meant to help you start your day right. When you first start your day accomplishing something meaningful or being positively affirmed, the rest of the day just goes so much better. This app will lift you up in the morning and give you advise for starting your day right.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
